      "role": "user",
      "content": "makes sense. so if the precautionary principle is the \"responsible\" way to go, does that mean the people pushing for rapid development are basically being reckless? i'm trying to figure out if there's a way to frame the accelerationist side as actually being proactive rather than just ignoring the risks.",
